metadata.title: CVE-2023-33546 on Ubuntu 22.10 (kinetic) - medium.
metadata.description: janino 3.1.9 and earlier are subject to denial of service (DOS) attacks when using the expression evaluator.guess parameter name method. If the parser runs on user-supplied input, an attacker could supply content that causes the parser to crash due to a stack overflow.

criterions.comment: janino package in kinetic is affected and may need fixing.
